    <rigor-reason>NFR-07 BINDING — pre-fill flow signatures + 45s timeout + `useAiPrefill` MUST remain UNCHANGED. Project-prefill flow is binding-sensitive in the same way as matter-prefill (task 034); any regression breaks production wizard. FULL rigor required: code-review + adr-check at Step 9.5 + explicit before/after pre-fill regression test.</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>B-G2</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>true</parallel-safe>
